hambered gun just as well as a chambered one. Again that is a personal preference and people who come to our family occasions follow those rules or they could feel safer by not coming. Plus the soldier story just happened today so thought it was worth mentioning. Brain dead people are everywhere, this happened by someone who has been knocked the gun rules repeatedly. We unfortunately can always expect the unpredictability of man.', 1, 0, '115.186.123.230', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
